Kindergarten
Registration for Kindergarten for the school year 2020-21 opens March 30, 2020.  To be eligible for kindergarten for the 2020-21 school year, a child must be five years old on or before Sept. 1, 2020.  Early Entrance into Kindergarten Information.

Early Entrance Procedures
CCPS early entrance procedures for prekindergarten, kindergarten and first grade.

Online registration for students new to CCPS entering prekindergarten through twelfth grade.  
Parents should use the registration link below to register a child not already enrolled in CCPS. Students currently enrolled do not need to register for the next school year. Due to the school closures, staff will not be available at schools and centers to assist with the registration process or uploading of documents until schools re-open.  Families unable to upload documents or complete other parts of the registration may start the process now and finish and submit it in the future.  Registrations can not be processed until all required documents have been uploaded.  Please email OLRsupport@.com with questions about online registration.



